  "intent_precise": "Nucleic Acid Extraction: Using magplate (plate, slot 2), elutionplate (plate, slot 3), res (reservoir, slot 5). With magnetic module. (1) Disengage magnets to release beads. (2) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination. (3) Mix 10 times at 30\u00b5L. (4) Incubate for 5 minutes. (5) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (6) Incubate for 3 minutes. (7) Transfer 60\u00b5L from source to destination. (8) Transfer 150\u00b5L from source to destination. (9) Incubate for 1 minutes. (10) Transfer 150\u00b5L from source to destination. (11) Incubate for 5 minutes. (12) Disengage magnets to release beads. (13) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source to destination. (14) Mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L. (15) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (16) Incubate for 5 minutes. (17) Transfer 50\u00b5L from source to destination. (18) Disengage magnets to release beads.",
